{"tid":1518802,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"「今日突發」眾人被拉一事證明好多和理非仲對警隊專業有幻想","createTime":"2019-08-30T11:02:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-30T12:32:49.000Z","uid":89974,"like":39,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"5bc82c274eb9f2c2cb92de49420f22f46033fcb7","tid":1518802,"uid":89974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T11:02:23.000Z","msg":"點解仲會有人因為社運人士無啦啦俾人拉而覺得震驚？<br />\n<br />\n我地面對緊既係<span style=\"color: red;\">無底線，無原則</span>既軍事組織，佢地每做既一步都係要打壓市民而唔係跟規例，佢地已經當咗所有市民係敵人，如果唔係殺人唔好睇，佢地晨早殺哂所有勇武而唔係打到佢地骨折就算。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">醒下啦！唔係黑警死就係所有香港人亡架啦！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<br />\n仲記唔記得<br />\n尻放催淚彈 <br />\n警棍亂毆人 <br />\n打到手足入廠 <br />\n放生黑社會 <br />\n開真槍<br />\n禁集會<br />\n拉街坊<br />\n射盲人<br />\n亂咁告人做白色恐怖<br />\n<br />\n仲記唔記得<br />\n大量人貪污逃稅<br />\n叫免費雞<br />\n警局入面強姦報害人<br />\nLan線自殺<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">呢團火已經無可能再熄，無一個正常人會甘願生活係咁既社會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n亦都唔駛擔心比人拉會留案底，一輸咗所有和理非都會俾人清算，相反贏咗就全世界特赦！大家勇敢啲企前多一步！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">解散警隊，審判黑警！</span></span>"},{"pid":"6fb73129c1033cd5a14d6d84850eb6c925521ab9","tid":1518802,"uid":89974,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T11:02:28.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">解散警隊，審判黑警！</span></span>"},{"pid":"ca8f2a8c6885e704c1d8273c8120639b98f0c6b4","tid":1518802,"uid":89974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T11:02:42.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">解散警隊，審判黑警！</span></span>"},{"pid":"f7797083def4447f6eea98952c47aab0fbc559fb","tid":1518802,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T11:02:57.000Z","msg":"幾句講哂<br />\n831無大台 自行選地點<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">901 1點鐘 機場見</span></span><br />\n92大三罷<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OvNBCkd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOvNBCkd.jpg&h=f0ee9ddd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">記住啊 我地只係幫機管局做交通壓力測試</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">901 機場 Channel</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=zmS1uFJnVw4lvQjuvPvUiv3ZlJXgeXtiTXALECG4O5Q%3D&h=3b9f327b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyou</a></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">901 機場 公海</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyouopen&d=zmS1uFJnVw4lvQjuvPvUiv3ZlJXgeXtiTXALECG4O5Q%3D&h=529f67d7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyouopen</a></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">901 機場 宣傳</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyoupromote\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyoupromote&d=zmS1uFJnVw4lvQjuvPvUiv3ZlJXgeXtiTXALECG4O5Q%3D&h=a59f8a12\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyoupromote</a></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">三罷 Channel</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><a href=\"http://T.me/hkgeneralstrike9293\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FT.me%2Fhkgeneralstrike9293&d=zmS1uFJnVw4lvQjuvPvUiv3ZlJXgeXtiTXALECG4O5Q%3D&h=f444dd87\" data-